lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur are favourites to win the Premier League this season according to table-topping Leicester City manager Claudio Ranieri, because their title charge has virtually gone under the radar.

headline.print_headline: Spurs Are Title Favourites, Says Leicester's Ranieri
